rsary celebrations, continues to generate attention for its political associations, unique setting and high-profile guest list.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/international-sports/several-a-list-celebrities-reportedly-reject-invitations-to-attend-dana-whites-trump-linked-ufc-event/articleshow/131563684.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/international-sports/several-a-list-celebrities-reportedly-reject-invitations-to-attend-dana-whites-trump-linked-ufc-event/articleshow/131563684.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-07T14:51:44+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Sports Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131564349,imgsize-95674.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['The diamond was gorgeous': Jill Biden wanted to keep PM Modi's $20,000 gift but couldn't afford it]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131563917.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/the-diamond-was-gorgeous-jill-biden-wanted-to-keep-pm-modis-20000-gift-but-couldnt-afford-it/articleshow/131563917.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/the-diamond-was-gorgeous-jill-biden-wanted-to-keep-pm-modis-20000-gift-but-couldnt-afford-it/articleshow/131563917.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-07T14:19:55+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131564112,imgsize-64248.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Gunshots, screams &amp; panic - Ohio mass shooting caught on cam, several injured]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131564087.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Panic erupted near Toledo's Old West End Festival on Saturday as gunfire injured at least 12 people, with two in critical condition. Authorities suspect multiple shooters, possibly exchanging fire. The incident, which saw festival-goers fleeing for safety, is under ongoing investigation. Governor DeWine emphasized the need for safe community events.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/gunshots-screams-panic-ohio-mass-shooting-caught-on-cam-several-injured/articleshow/131564087.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/gunshots-screams-panic-ohio-mass-shooting-caught-on-cam-several-injured/articleshow/131564087.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-07T14:32:45+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131564392,imgsize-9176444.cms"/></item></channel></rss>